title: Giulio Cesare, il conquistatore delle Gallie (1962)

sources.title: Giulio Cesare, il conquistatore delle Gallie (1962)
sources.description: In 54 B.C. Julius Caesar seeks to solidify his position in Rome by putting down a rebellion in Gaul led by a tribal chieftain named Vercingetorix. Vercingetorix has rallied many tribes to his cause, including one led by the beautiful Queen Asterid and others who'd once pledged allegiance to Rome.
